{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事Barr：通膨率可能仍在3% 降息問題上需謹慎行事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>理事Michael Barr表示，在通膨仍比目標高出一個百分點的情況下，央行在考慮進一步降息時需保持謹慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barr周四在華盛頓的一場活動上表示：「我擔心通膨率仍在3%左右，而我們的目標是2%，聯儲會承諾要實現這一目標。因此，我們現在在制定貨幣政策時必須小心謹慎，確保實現雙重使命的平衡。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barr可能成為12月9-10日聯儲會政策會議上的關鍵一票。多位官員已表態支持或反對連續第三次降息，這使會議結果充滿不確定性。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6440f1c1-0ad1-35b7-aa49-43f9e96608c2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周四上午最新就業數據公佈後，Barr表示，他認為勞動力市場「正在趨於降溫」，新增就業接近維持失業率穩定的平衡水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說：「總體而言，勞動力市場處於一種相對平衡的狀態，但這種平衡是在淨新增就業數量相當低的基礎上實現的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據美國勞工統計局的數據，9月份新增就業11.9萬個，失業率小幅上升至4.4%。這份因政府停擺而推遲發布的就業報告是聯儲會官員在下次會議前將看到的最後一份就業數據。根據聯邦基金利率期貨的定價，投資者目前預計12月降息的概率約為40%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國9月非農報告出爐：就業轉增且失業率微升</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Barr Says Fed Must Move Carefully With Inflation Still at 3%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8Bbarr-%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E7%8E%87%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A83-%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E9%9C%80%E8%AC%B9%E6%85%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%8B-153721434.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 00:05:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "克利夫蘭聯儲行長：為支撐就業而降息可能延長通膨並加劇風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Cleveland Fed President Beth Hammack.\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3Kr5e3sU2qaI4f19r.eaSw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5253bfa5ede8e81d71ac37ee5154c1ec\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Cleveland Fed President Beth Hammack.</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 克利夫蘭聯邦儲備銀行行長Beth Hammack表示，為支撐勞動力市場而降息可能會令通膨在更長時間內高於目標水平，並增加金融穩定風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Hammack;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Hammack\">Hammack</a>在周四一場書面演講中表示，近期股市上漲和信貸環境寬鬆使投資者更傾向於冒險，這將加劇風險。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"克利夫蘭聯儲行長Beth Hammack攝影：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hU2SUqrswPG6QxmE67B38A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/16c5a11f3ecb0305125de2e947ba5138\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">克利夫蘭聯儲行長Beth Hammack攝影：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「為了支撐勞動力市場而降低利率可能會延長當前的高通膨時期，也可能鼓勵金融市場中的風險偏好。」她說，「這意味著，一旦下一輪經濟下行來臨，規模可能會比原本更大，對經濟的衝擊也將更深。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-144460a7-8b71-3c79-802c-90b049560fb1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammack此前表示，決策者應繼續對通膨保持下行壓力以將其拉回聯儲會2%的目標。她反對10月的降息決定，並認為12月幾乎沒有理由再次降息。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Hammack Says Rate Cuts May Prolong Inflation, Boost Risks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%8B%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%AB%E8%98%AD%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7-%E7%82%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%92%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E4%B8%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-142401143.html",
