        {
            "title": "隨著美國關稅引發的動盪消退 德國央行預計第四季度德國經濟有望成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"657\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aEXGSbEVW0BrDtG62zLDHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9cadffc3a6828cb3b6139a2476ce1004\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國央行表示，隨著美國關稅引發的動盪逐漸消退，德國經濟可能在今年最後三個月重回成長軌道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行在周三發布的月度報告中指出，2025年初出口激增，隨後在後續數月轉為拖累因素，預計出口和工業將在「第四季度趨於穩定」。報告稱，服務業也將支撐經濟活動，「儘管未必來自消費相關領域」。德國央行表示，這可能使得整體產出「小幅成長」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"657\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rDq4GDqxy44YNxWv_JeWMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ba43b2cf88fc182791283bbddcbb5efd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲最大經濟體德國在第三季度陷入停滯，幾乎沒有跡象表明其能從2023年和2024年產出萎縮的長期疲軟中復甦。面對美國加徵關稅和中國競爭加劇的局面，德國總理弗里德里希·默茨正試圖通過投入數千億歐元用於基礎設施和國防建設來推動經濟反彈。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ea49b8a5-46e0-39cb-8804-f76bdd2f96b6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德國央行表示，這種財政寬鬆政策對建築業和投資的持續影響要到明年才會顯現。當前德國競爭力持續惡化，使其僅能有限度地受益於全球成長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，疲軟的勞動力市場拖累私人消費。報告指出，製造業大幅裁員，儘管其他「受益於人口結構變化和能源轉型」的行業有所成長，帶來了一定的緩衝。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Germany on Track for Growth in Fourth Quarter, Bundesbank Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9A%A8%E8%91%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E6%B6%88%E9%80%80-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-114042358.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 20:31:02",
