        },
        {
            "title": "德國財長稱中國行幫助兩國彌合分歧 獲得了中方關於稀土供應的承諾",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"841\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.oUISjTFS.t6O2bXMU8K4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2bd8c5ca07888485fcb116e890381279\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國財政部長拉爾斯·克林拜爾表示，他已獲得中方關於維持關鍵原物料供應的保證，並稱這是他本周為期四天的亞洲之行中最重要的成果。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「最關鍵的是，中方就稀土和關鍵原物料問題、可靠的獲取渠道和供應鏈作出了明確承諾，中方將恪守這一承諾，」<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:克林拜爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/克林拜爾\">克林拜爾</a>周四在新加坡對記者表示。「這是非常關鍵的一點，是公開承諾的，我們將提醒中方這一點。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中德兩國作為全球三大經濟體中的兩個成員，正尋求翻過關係緊張的一頁。近幾個月來，隨著中國收緊出口管制，以及德國外交部長Johann Wadephul因日程安排問題推遲訪華計畫，兩國貿易摩擦持續加劇。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-612d5af4-c8f0-31fa-9126-29ee7bf535e3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">克林拜爾提及的協議細節不足，中方是否會兌現承諾也有待觀察。鑒於德國和歐盟對中國的經濟依賴程度，雙方幾乎沒有施壓的籌碼；中國生產全球大部分的稀土。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"841\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cMqRkBk.nQoxVBqLzYHXWQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e90b8905e9aa03be15ec7773902e98b7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，據知情人士透露，克林拜爾呼籲中國推動結束俄烏戰爭的努力未能成功。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周早些時候在北京與國務院副總理何立峰等官員會晤後，克林拜爾周四表示，中方還同意考慮放寬德國銀行和保險公司進入中國金融市場的准入條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">克林拜爾與何立峰共同出席了中德財金對話，該會議包含與當地監管機構及金融機構的圓桌會議環節。隨行的德國銀行業代表包括國有開發銀行KfW、德國商業銀行和德意志銀行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">克林拜爾表示：「隨行的德國企業也提出了若干構想，表示希望加強在中國市場的佈局。中國方面也承諾將考慮所有這些想法。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在訪問北京和上海之後，克林拜爾將行程收官站定在新加坡，會見了包括總理黃循財在內的政府官員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">克林拜爾表示，新加坡「面臨著非常相似的挑戰」，並希望與德國開展合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他們向我們提出了加強合作的意向，」他說。「他們希望實現供應鏈多元化，擺脫現有依賴，尋求與德國建立密切聯繫。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題German Finance Chief Says China Trip Helped Bridge Differences</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B9%AB%E5%8A%A9%E5%85%A9%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%8C%E5%90%88%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7-%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E7%A8%80%E5%9C%9F%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E7%9A%84%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE-100009046.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 18:55:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "渾水的Block表示現在不宜做空美國大型科技股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"689\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fT2j0VAjdgfBcQ21_L16jA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0828620bce697930868ed1e89feda71e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 賣空投資者Carson Block認為現在還不是做空美國大型科技公司的時候，儘管人們越來越擔心人工智能AI領域可能存在泡沫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在這個市場，我寧願做多而不是做空。」渾水資本執行長Block在接受彭博電視採訪時說道，「如果你試圖做空輝達或任何其他大型科技公司，你的生意不會長久。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"689\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7b.pyUpuOtBsaX8O68JbKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/eda546e1425c66984cb37436d749839b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Block表示，他正在關注一些AI領域的小型公司，以尋找潛在的做空機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「現在有很多AI外圍公司，或者說是AI的冒牌貨，這些才是你應該做空的目標。」他說道，「但是，只要像輝達這樣的領頭羊股價還在上漲，做空就非常危險。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d9a9bb87-ce15-378a-a3ca-6740f1749d62-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「輝達股價漲到多高都無所謂。」他說，「所有買入標普500指數的基金，在出現資金淨流出之前都不會賣出輝達股票。只要有資金流入，他們就會每天買入，不管價格怎麼樣。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周三Block披露了難得的多頭頭寸，他做多了加拿大礦業公司Snowline Gold Corp.，後者股價一度上漲了23%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Muddy Waters’ Block Says It’s Not the Time to Short Big Tech</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Anna Edwards、Guy Johnson、Farah Elbahrawy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%BE%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84block%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%81%9A%E7%A9%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%82%A1-095842250.html",
